data.description: This statuesque home with an attractive curb appeal is in the beautifully cared for neighborhood of prestigious Holland Acres is in Northampton Township and Council Rock School district, one of the best ranked in PA with the school bus stop steps away for priceless convenience. Brand new windows and doors throughout the home updated in January 2022 with warranty transfers to the new buyer.  As you open the front door, you are greeted by an impressive vaulted ceiling complete with chandelier, newly installed luxury vinyl plank with marble look all while comfortable to walk on barefoot in winter, thick plank real hardwood flooring, spiral staircase leading to the 2nd floor. The magnificent foyer is flanked by the living room with cozy 1st real wood fireplace on the left and the spacious dining room on the right. There is so much to offer in this unique and versatile home. As you continue down the center hall, the kitchen with center island and breakfast nook leads to the family room with 2nd real wood fireplace opening to the atrium w/cathedral ceiling, wood beams and atrium/office doors to wrap around custom decking. This memorable home is full of amenities and generous living spaces. The full, finished basement has an exercise room, media room and a walk-in cedar closet. The 4 bedrooms are generous and inviting. The huge garage is also equipped with a full bathroom that opens up to the outside and can be used as a pool bath.  An entrance from the backyard makes it easy to use the bathroom/changing room after a refreshing swim. The beautiful heated in-ground pool is complete with a spa, surrounding walkways and sitting areas and a gazebo to relax in the evening. Corner lot with almost an acre is a rare find. Circular driveway with plenty of parking for large gatherings.  Tons of upgrades. Sellers are relocating and motivated! Showing only to pre approved and serious buyers.
data.whatILove: *Back on the Market* Great curb appeal, large backyard pool, large spacious lot, great home for entertaining, safe friendly neighborhood, true gem of a home!
